<h1>Wholesale voice for organizations that care about performance and cost visibility.</h1>
<p class="lede"><a href="/voice/">VoiceTel Wholesale Voice</a> is built for managed service providers, carriers, operators, and organizations that need inbound and outbound voice with published rate keys, routing controls, and escalation paths.</p>
<p>The platform supports origination and termination, Anycast, Geocast, and diverse routing. These routing approaches are positioned around performance, resiliency, localized delivery, and business continuity.</p>
